Name: Vanguard Princess
About the game: Government experiments on a young girl triggered a cosmic shock wave that gifted many young girls with mystical powers. She re-emerges into the world and vows to destroy all of mankind in an act of revenge. A brave group of girls who embraced their powers heads to the battlefield to confront her; not just for the sake of the world, but to pursue their own personal motives and dreams. Choose from ten girls with unique fighting skills and pair them with a powerful partner to form an unstoppable team. Navigate the adventures of a Vanguard Princess in the Story Mode or engage in head-to-head battles in the Versus Mode. / / /
